      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i'm just really worried cuz my leg has been feeling kinda swollen and sore since i landed too. u sure its just the air pressure/stress? i dont really want to go to a hospital in a foreign city if i dont have to, it seems like a lot of hassle just for anxiety.",
