    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that's a relief. i was getting really freaked out. so as long as i just keep walking and maybe take some ibuprofen if it keeps hurting i should be fine? i'll just try to relax and get to my hotel. u think i'm totally safe to just sleep this off?",
